From 0.3.7 to 0.3.8:
  * replaced Eclipse-generated makefiles with automake+autoconf ones.
    new 'configure' script also autodetects required C functions and headers
  
  * fstransform: added better checks for devices with last odd-sized block,
    now create loop-file length is device size _rounded_down_
    to file-system block size
    
  * fsremap: added better checks for devices with last odd-sized block,
    now it refuses to run if loop-file is larger than device size _rounded_down_
    to file-system block size
  
  * fsmove: added progress report
